plot

# logFC
foldChange <- DEGs$logFC
names(foldChange) <- DEGs$nameOfGene

cnetplot(GOBP,
         foldChange = foldChange,
         showCategory = 10,
         cex_label_gene = 0.5, # 
         cex_label_category = 0.8 # pathway
         )

cnetplot(GOBP,
         foldChange = foldChange,
         showCategory = 5,
         cex_label_gene = 0.5, # 
         cex_label_category = 0.5, # pathway
         circular = TRUE, # 
         colorEdge = TRUE, # edge
         )

DEGs <- read.csv(file = "edgeR_DGE.csv")
dim(DEGs)
## [1] 10542     6
head(DEGs)
# logFC * -log10(p.value) value
DEGs$value <- DEGs$logFC * -log10(DEGs$PValue)

valueclusterProfiler
value

geneRank <- DEGs$value
names(geneRank) <- DEGs$nameOfGene

head(geneRank)
##    ATP2A1  SH3BGRL2      PYGM     PTHLH     SASH1     PTGFR 
## -67.43322 -59.86737 -76.89569  57.11429 -43.07500 -63.91542

geneRank <- sort(geneRank, decreasing = TRUE)
head(geneRank)
